{"tid":1062703,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗蟲當眾方便　目擊者︰呢啲咩阿媽！","createTime":"2019-03-15T09:09:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-15T10:00:19.000Z","uid":225464,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"bf21baa508ce63edd8cd73659e1cfce93f7e9092","tid":1062703,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:09:28.000Z","msg":"<strong>餐廳內當眾方便 女童爆喊 目擊者︰呢啲咩阿媽！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Y0dLBW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Y0dLBW&d=1zr6t4yB9inWhfXylFPsaQogPkW5zMkxdNnzPoGklno%3D&h=42daeae3\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Y0dLBW</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190315/photo/bkn-20190315153210444-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190315155930\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190315%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190315153210444-0315_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190315155930&h=4ecd60c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會對女童心理造成幾大影響？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n常言道︰「喺度食，唔好喺度屙。」惟近日旺角有媽媽竟帶備痰罐，讓女兒在快餐店當眾「方便」，事後更疑把盛着排泄物的膠袋丟在地上？<br />\n<br />\n有網友周五（15日）在Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」發貼，指在旺角中心一間連鎖快餐店用膳時，發現有女童在餐廳的柱子旁脫下褲子，坐在痰罐上當眾如廁。<br />\n<br />\n該網友形容︰「真係呆咗！呢個真係仆X過喺街度便溺！無晒胃口呀！個小朋友仲要喊，好唔願意。真係呢啲咩阿媽」！<br />\n<br />\n該媽媽事後疑把盛着排泄物的膠袋「藏」在座位下。近半小時後，餐廳經理出現，着他們自行收拾該袋垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n網友紛紛怒斥：「黐線」、「個阿媽寧願吹水都唔帶個女去洗手間，點做人阿媽呀」、「見到個細路咁樣好心痛」、「明明隔籬已經有公廁」。"},{"pid":"64b6a167b3e45bea763fdd08ef5b3c074040f8e8","tid":1062703,"uid":27451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"又係蝗，唔意外啦"},{"pid":"248443b3557321178e867f12c74e0675b76e26ea","tid":1062703,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T09:12:22.000Z","msg":"猜猜她們在說甚麼話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e477320844c3e27f7e5755b0e173fa472a0ca5f7","tid":1062703,"uid":142313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-15T10:00:19.000Z","msg":"我屋企好似仲有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}